623
00:46:58.690 --> 00:47:00.233
Damn, you're good.

624
00:47:05.614 --> 00:47:07.073
You are good.

625
00:47:50.659 --> 00:47:51.784
Good morning. Listen up.

626
00:47:51.952 --> 00:47:56.038
