and the airports on him.

630
00:48:13.807 --> 00:48:18.311
Detective Malone just transferred.
He'll head our Burglary division.

631
00:48:19.313 --> 00:48:20.605
Detective...

632
00:48:20.814 --> 00:48:22.982
