751
00:55:38.668 --> 00:55:39.877
Shit!

752
00:55:59.439 --> 00:56:01.023
Evidence room.

753
00:56:01.358 --> 00:56:02.399
Shit!

754
00:56:05.945 --> 00:56:08.947
There you are. l just got a call.

755
00:56:09.199 --> 00:56:10.783
41 3 in progress
at the airport.

